Episode #4: Short Arrow Functions

Episode 4 — Short Arrow Functions — Nikita Popov





Arrow functions have the following basic form:


fn(parameter_list) => expr


Traditional Closure:


$arrow = function ($x) use ($y) {
    return $x + $y;
};







New Short Closure:


$arrow = fn($x) => $x + $y;




https://wiki.php.net/rfc/arrow_functions_v2 — https://github.com/php/php-src/pull/3941/files
